115
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,120
Um...

116
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,720
Like this?
Clean at the bow?

117
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:22,160
...You know...
...No net cutter?

118
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,360
It was just a couple of seconds.
I really couldn't say for...

119
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:27,120
So you were... you were on
lookout that night, mister...

120
