125
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:38,960
About 300 patients.

126
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:42,160
At least that many.

127
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,880
Out of North Africa.

128
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:47,360
Yeah, plus over 70 hands crew.

129
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,480
So, um...

130
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,360
You said they fired
only one torpedo?

131
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:51,360
O'Dell...

132
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:53,040
you better tell sonar we've got
an enemy sub in the area.

133
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,400
Yes, sir.
Just let me finish...

134
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,560
Now. Do it now.

135
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:56,600
Yes, sir.

136
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:03,200
I'm... I'm sorry that
we couldn't save more. I...

137
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:07,120
Now this... the third member
of your party, he's...

138
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,680
One of my patients.

139
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:12,000
Well, under normal
circumstances,

140
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:14,880
I'd be able to drop you
at the nearest port in England,

141
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:17,440
