humane treatment!

250
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:08,200
He has a wife and family.

251
00:20:08,280 --> 00:20:10,440
He wants to get home
just like you or me.

252
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:12,480
Everything will be all right.

253
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:22,400
