01:06:42,640 --> 01:06:43,880
Loomis...

821
01:06:45,600 --> 01:06:47,440
I-I, um...

822
01:06:47,520 --> 01:06:49,200
Go ahead.

823
01:06:49,280 --> 01:06:51,360
