wanted to help.

858
01:12:14,600 --> 01:12:17,360
Apparently Captain Winters
lost the argument.

859
01:12:17,440 --> 01:12:19,840
Well, that's interesting.

860
01:12:21,680 --> 01:12:26,200
But it's not what I heard...
from Mr. Brice.

861
01:12:28,480 --> 01:12:31,280
Lieutenant?

862
01:12:31,360 --> 01:12:34,000
