...Stumbo. Stumbo!

894
01:14:06,640 --> 01:14:08,840
...Let me try.
...We already bought it.

895
01:14:08,880 --> 01:14:10,320
Come on, Stumbo. Head up.

896
01:14:10,400 --> 01:14:12,240
...Over and over...
...I need you to sit up.

897
01:14:12,320 --> 01:14:14,120
...over and over again.
...Look at me.

898
01:14:14,200 --> 01:14:15,640
Now look at me.
Look at me.

899
01:14:15,720 --> 01:14:17,240
...Good.

