...Whoa, hey, hey, hey! Hey!

904
01:14:25,640 --> 01:14:28,000
...Take it easy! Hey!
...Relax, man!

905
01:14:28,080 --> 01:14:29,800
Stumbo!

906
01:14:29,840 --> 01:14:32,680
Isn't there a winch or a pulley

907
01:14:32,720 --> 01:14:34,720
