in a bowsman's locker?

908
01:14:34,800 --> 01:14:35,840
...Yeah.
...Can't we use that?

909
01:14:35,920 --> 01:14:37,320
You know what he's
talking about, Stumbo?

910
01:14:37,360 --> 01:14:38,720
...Yeah.
...Well, come on.

911
01:14:38,760 --> 01:14:41,160
Come... we need it. Come on.
Show... show me, Stumbo.

912
01:14:41,240 --> 01:14:43,240
We've got to get it.
Okay, come on. Come on.

913
01:14:46,640 --> 01:14:48,920
So, tell me
why three officers

914
01:14:49,000 --> 01:14:51,840
would conspire to kill
their captain

915
01:14:51,920 --> 01:14:54,120
and cover it up.

916
01:14:54,160 --> 01:14:56,240
That's what you're thinking,
isn't it?

917
01:14:56,320 --> 01:14:57,840
What if I am?

918
01:14:57,920 --> 01:15:00,000
I can see I'm not the only one.

919
01:15:02,480 --> 01:15:04,960
Loomis was up
for a major citation.

920
01:15:05,040 --> 01:15:06,920
And Brice was ready
for his own command.

921
01:15:07,000 --> 01:15:09,240
He was from a naval family.
He went to Annapolis.

922
01:15:09,320 --> 01:15:11,680
Coors had this beautiful girl
waiting for him back in Boston

923
01:15:11,720 --> 01:15:13,440
that he was always
talking about, Claire.

924
01:15:13,480 --> 01:15:15,880
These guys had everything
to live for.

925
01:15:15,960 --> 01:15:20,280
By that reasoning...
they had everything to lose.

926
01:15:26,080 --> 01:15:28,240
Are we missing somebody?

927
01:15:44,160 --> 01:15:45,600
Wallace...

928
01:15:47,560 --> 01:15:49,000
Wallace?

929
01:15:50,520 --> 01:15:51,440
...No!

930
01:15:51,520 --> 01:15:52,960
...No! No!
...Shh!

931
01:15:53,040 --> 01:15:55,320
...No-o-o!
...It's just us.

932
01:15:55,400 --> 01:15:57,320
It's just... us.

933
01:15:57,400 --> 01:15:59,880
...Now, listen...

934
01:15:59,960 --> 01:16:02,360
We're running out of plays
in the playbook.

935
01:16:02,440 --> 01:16:05,080
Do you have... any idea
why the boat is going back

936
01:16:05,160 --> 01:16:07,880
or how we can get control
of it?

937
01:16:09,080 --> 01:16:11,160
I've been checking the
literature on this subject.

938
01:16:11,240 --> 01:16:13,400
And the thing we know
about maledictions is...

939
01:16:13,480 --> 01:16:14,520
Maledictions?

940
01:16:14,600 --> 01:16:15,680
Look it up.

941
01:16:15,760 --> 01:16:17,920
Maledictions don't issue
from Heaven or Hell

942
01:16:17,960 --> 01:16:20,360
