in between.

943
01:16:20,440 --> 01:16:22,000
I n fact, there's a great...

944
01:16:22,080 --> 01:16:24,240
Wallace...
we're running out of air.

945
01:16:26,240 --> 01:16:29,040
Suffice to say...

946
01:16:29,120 --> 01:16:33,440
the malediction needs
satisfaction

947
01:16:33,520 --> 01:16:36,200
in order to escape
its netherworld.

948
01:16:36,240 --> 01:16:38,920
And if you had to guess...

949
01:16:38,960 --> 01:16:42,400
what would satisfy
our malediction?

950
01:16:42,480 --> 01:16:44,440
Old Man Winters never
got a chance

951
01:16:44,520 --> 01:16:45,920
to go down with the ship,
did he?

952
01:16:54,640 --> 01:16:56,040
Wallace, leave yours here.

953
01:16:56,080 --> 01:16:58,120
We gotta dig up
some more light.

954
01:16:58,200 --> 01:16:59,480
Okay, listen, uh...

955
01:16:59,560 --> 01:17:03,720
Just... Just promise me
you'll stay on your feet, okay?

956
01:17:15,800 --> 01:17:17,480
"Don't pretend..."

