982
01:21:47,480 --> 01:21:50,080
Not when he left us
in the water to die.

983
01:21:50,120 --> 01:21:53,160
Not when he heard the cries
for help in English.

984
01:21:53,240 --> 01:21:54,120
You actually believe

985
01:21:54,200 --> 01:21:56,240
