just leave...

986
01:21:56,320 --> 01:21:58,720
Help! Help me!

987
01:21:58,760 --> 01:22:00,320
No.

988
01:22:00,360 --> 01:22:03,880
Captain Winters wanted to
pick up the survivors.

989
01:22:04,880 --> 01:22:05,800
That means...

